## Mac Gaming DB
MacGamingDB is a website for Mac gamers, it's a database of game performance reviews across different Mac configurations and Translation layers like CrossOver, Parallels, etc.

## Tech Stack
- Next.js
- Shadcn/ui
- Tailwind CSS
- Prisma
- BetterAuth
- Vercel
- Bun
- TypeScript
- React Email

