## Code Rules
- No `any` type
- No deeply nested if else, extract generic logic to utility function, only one function per file and one export.
- Respect existing code style and patterns.
- No hacky code low quality code.


Always use Bun for package manager and for running scripts.
```
bun add <package>
bun run <script>
```
